  1. Define a function called add_tree that takes a single argument and returns a value 3 times larger than the input.
add_tree <- function() {
  argument = readline(prompt= "enter a number to recove a value 3 times larger : ")
  argument = as.integer(argument)
  print(argument*3)
}
